data.description: Beautifully done custom home with circular drive, large portico, RV parking, a fully fenced backyard and tons of living space. At nearly 2,600 square feet, this home sprawls across the property, with large trees providing shade from the summer heat, with a detached garage, connected by a breezeway, fruit trees in the spacious back yard. This property also boasts 2 jacuzzi bathtubs. The sale of this property is subject to the approval of Nye county probate court.
